OL,13,     Gscientists is hunted by a
OL,14,     Gmonstrous force in Norman J.
OL,15,     GWarren's cult sci-fi horror. Once
OL,16,     Glabeled a notorious 'video
OL,17,     Gnasty,' it blends terror, gore,
OL,18,     Gand wild fun.
